107
00:04:29,435 --> 00:04:33,320
Because I looked in the bed,
and there are no bugs.

108
00:04:33,322 --> 00:04:34,622
Aw, I love you, too.

109
00:04:34,624 --> 00:04:36,940
If I don't talk to you
before you go to sleep,

110
00:04:36,942 --> 00:04:38,909
I'll meet you in dreamland.

111
00:04:38,911 --> 00:04:40,161
AMY:
Good night.

112
00:04:40,163 --> 00:04:43,464
No, I will not consider sleeping
in my garment bag.

113
00:04:46,818 --> 00:04:50,588
Penny, did you ever wonder
how Starfleet captains...

114
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:52,773
No.

115
00:04:54,593 --> 00:04:56,811
Well, now that I've piqued
your interest,

116
00:04:56,813 --> 00:04:59,764
