his significance in my life.

122
00:05:08,991 --> 00:05:10,241
Oh...

123
00:05:10,243 --> 00:05:12,359
Do I miss
how he makes a face

124
00:05:12,361 --> 00:05:14,645
on my toaster waffle
with syrup?

125
00:05:14,647 --> 00:05:16,230
No.

126
00:05:16,232 --> 00:05:18,532
Do I miss the way

127
00:05:18,534 --> 00:05:21,452
