when it gets stuck?

128
00:05:21,454 --> 00:05:23,537
(chuckles)
I don't think so.

129
00:05:23,539 --> 00:05:25,589
Do I miss how
we say "good night"

130
00:05:25,591 --> 00:05:28,042
to each other through the walls
of our bedroom

131
00:05:28,044 --> 00:05:29,410
