than the old, ugly ones.

162
00:06:57,365 --> 00:06:58,799
Mr. Wolowitz,

163
00:06:58,801 --> 00:06:59,850
Dr. Koothrappali.

164
00:06:59,852 --> 00:07:01,268
Mrs. Davis,
nice to see you.

165
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:04,922
You know, I recently read
a fascinating article

166
00:07:04,924 --> 00:07:07,625
