167
00:07:07,627 --> 00:07:10,227
Okay.

168
00:07:10,229 --> 00:07:12,863
So if the fact
that your husband left you

169
00:07:12,865 --> 00:07:14,765
makes you feel unattractive,
just remember,

170
00:07:14,767 --> 00:07:17,801
