of autobiographical memory.

176
00:07:41,894 --> 00:07:43,844
Oh, brain lesions
are fascinating.

177
00:07:43,846 --> 00:07:46,931
Unless they're yours,
then they're a drag.

178
00:07:46,933 --> 00:07:49,466
To the advancement of science.

179
00:07:49,468 --> 00:07:52,569
And to the sick and dying
who make it possible.

180
00:07:54,689 --> 00:07:56,824
This is fun; we never
really get to talk shop

181
