conversation.

185
00:08:03,816 --> 00:08:06,433
From the two gentlemen
at the bar.

186
00:08:06,435 --> 00:08:08,035
Oh, my gosh, boys
bought us drinks!

187
00:08:08,037 --> 00:08:10,704
Boys bought us drinks!
(gibbering happily)

188
00:08:10,706 --> 00:08:12,573
Thank you, thank you,
thank you so much.

189
00:08:13,959 --> 00:08:15,676
Be cool.
You be cool!

190
00:08:15,678 --> 00:08:18,762
