from below.

196
00:08:35,147 --> 00:08:37,231
So that means I lose, right?

197
00:08:37,233 --> 00:08:38,866
It's over!

198
00:08:38,868 --> 00:08:42,269
If I make this move...

199
00:08:42,271 --> 00:08:45,789
but I won't because we're having
too much fun.

200
00:08:46,591 --> 00:08:49,460
Okay, let's take a break.

201
00:08:49,462 --> 00:08:52,379
