202
00:08:52,381 --> 00:08:54,014
I wasn't going to get alcohol.

203
00:08:54,016 --> 00:08:56,550
(groans)

204
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,504
(sighs)

205
00:09:00,506 --> 00:09:02,256
Gosh, I wonder what
Leonard's doing right now.

206
00:09:02,258 --> 00:09:04,558
I miss him so much.

207
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:06,209
Well, if you'd like,

208
00:09:06,211 --> 00:09:07,594
